[{"Id": 1015797, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Offer 2 rakat namaz with the intension of “Namaz-e-Tawaf” in its 1st Rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Ikhlaas> and in 2nd Rakat after <Surah Fateha> recite <Surah Kaafiroon>. After namaz one should praise Allah and send salutations on Mohammed and his progeny. One should pray for its acceptance and say…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Namaz-e-Tawaaf ki 1st rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad <Surah Ikhlaas> aur 2nd rakat mein <Surah Fateha> ke baad <Surah Kaafiroon> padhna mustahab hai. Namaz ke baad Khuda ki hamd o sana kare, Muhammad (s) wa Aale Muhammad (a) par salawaat bheje aur Khuda wande aalam se dua kare keh uske amaal ko sharaf-e-qabooliyyat ataa farmaaye aur phir kahe…", "UrduDescription": "۲ رکعت نماز طواف کہ جس کی پہلی رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد <سورۂ اخلاص> اور دوسری رکعت میں <سورۂ فاتحہ> کے بعد <سورۂ کافرون> پڑھنا مستحب ہے نماز کے بعد اللہ کی حمد و ثنا کرے، محمدؐ و آل محمدؑ پر صلوات بھیجے اور خداوند عالم سے دُعا کرے کہ اس کے عمل کو شرف قبولیت عطا فرمائے اور پھر کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015798, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Allah! Tu mujhe se yeh qabool kar aur usey mera aakhri tawaaf qaraar na de. Allah ke liye Uski tamaam neymato’n par, tamaam taarife’n hai, yahan tak yeh hamd us darje tak pohonch jaaye jise Woh pasand kare aur raazi ho jaaye. Ay Allah! Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki Aale Paak (a.s) par durood naazil farma aur mujh se yeh ibaadat qabool kar, mere dil aur amal ko paakeeza kar de.", "Urdu": "اے اللہ! تو مجھ سے یہ قبول کر اور اسے میرا آخری طواف نہ قرار دے۔ اللہ کے لئے اس کی تمام نعمتوں پر، تمام تعریفیں ہیں، یہاں تک یہ حمد اس درجہ تک پہونچ جائے جسے وہ پسند کرے اور راضی ہو جائے۔ اے اللہ! محمدؐ اور ان کی آلؑ پر درود نازل فرما اور مجھ سے یہ عبادت قبول کر، میرے دل اور عمل کو پاکیزہ کردے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA TAQABBAL MINNEE WA LAA TAJ-A’LHO AAKHERAL A’HDE MINNEE AL-HAMDO LILLAAHE BEMAHAAMEDEHI KULLEHAA A’LAA NA’MAAA-EHI KULLEHAA HATTAA YANTAHEYAL HAMDO ELAA MAA YOHIBBO WA YARZAA ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIWN WA AALEHI WA TAQABBAL MINNEE WA TAHHIR QALBEE WA ZAKKE A’MALEE.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰہُمَّ تَقَبَّلْ مِنِّیْ وَلَا تَجْعَلْہُ آخِرَ الْعَہْدِ مِنِّیْ۔ اَلْحَمْدُ لِلہِ بِمَحَامَدِہٖ كُلِّہَا عَلٰی نَعْمَآئِہٖ كُلِّہَا حَتّٰی یَنْتَہِیَ الْحَمْدُ اِلٰی مَا یُحِبُّ وَیَرْضٰی۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِہٖ وَتَقَبَّلْ مِنِّیْ وَطَہِّرْ قَلْبِیْ وَزَكِّ عَمَلِیْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015799, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "According to another tradition one should say…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Dusri riwaayat ke mutaabiq is tarah se kahe…", "UrduDescription": "دوسری روایت کے مطابق یہ کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015800, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay mere Allah! Khaas kar Teri aur Tere Rasool (s.a.w.a) ki ita’at karne ki bina par mujh par rehmat farma. Khudaaya! Mujhe us baat se bacha keh mai Tere muqarrar shudah hudood se tajaawuz karu aur mujhe un logo’n mein qaraar de jo Tujhe aur Tere Rasool (s.a.w.a) ko Tere malaayeka ko aur Tere saaleh bando’n ko dost rakhte hai.", "Urdu": "اے میرے اللہ! خاص کر تیری اور تیرے رسولؐ کی اطاعت کرنے کی بنا پر مجھ پر رحم فرما۔ خدایا! مجھے اس بات سے بچا کہ میں تیرے مقررہ حدود سے تجاوز کروں اور مجھے ان لوگوں میں قرار دے جو تجھے اور تیرے رسولؐ کو تیرے ملائکہ کو اور تیرے صالح بندوں کو دوست رکھتے ہیں۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMAR HAMNEE BE-TAA-A’TEE IYYAAKA WA TAA-A’TE RASOOLEKA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI WA SALLAMA ALLAAHUMMA JANNIBNEE AN ATA-A’DDAA HODOODAKA WAJ-A’LNEE MIMMAN YOHIBBOKA WA YOHIBBO RASOOLAKA WA MALAAA-EKATAKA WA E’BADAKAS SAALEHEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰہُمَّ ارْحَمْنِیْ بِطَاعَتِیْ اِیَّاكَ وَطَاعَۃِ رَسُولِكَ صَلَّی اللہُ عَلَیْہِ وَآلِہٖ وَسَلَّمَ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ جَنِّبْنِیْ اَنْ اَتَعَدّٰی حُدُوْدَكَ وَاجْعَلْنِیْ مِمَّنْ یُحِبُّكَ وَیُحِبُّ رَسُوْلَكَ وَمَلَآئِكَتَكَ وَعِبَادَكَ الصَّالِحِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015801, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 3, "EnglishDescription": "Another narration states that Imam Sadiq (a) used to perform prostration after the prayer of circumambulation and say…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Baaz riwaayat mein hai keh Imam Jafar Sadiq (a) Namaz-e-Tawaaf ke baad sajdeh mein ja kar yeh dua padhte thay…", "UrduDescription": "بعض روایات میں ہے کہ امام جعفر صادقؑ نماز طواف کے بعد سجدہ میں جا کر یہ دُعا پرھتے تھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015802, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Prostate myself before You in worship and service. It is the truth that there is no God except You. You were there before anything and will be there after everything perishes. I am before You and my forelock is in Your hands. Forgive my sins for there is none to forgive major sins except You. Forgive me as I confess my sins against myself and none can avert cardinal sins except You.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mere chehre ne bandagi aur ghulaami ki haalat mein Tera sajdah kiya, Tere alaawa koi haqeeqi Khuda nahi hai, Tu har cheez se pehle hai aur har cheez ke baad bhi hai. Mai Tere saamne hu, meri peshaani Tere haath (ikhteyaar) mein hai lehaaza Tu mujhe bakhsh de. Yaqeenan bade gunah ko Tere alaawa koi nahi bakhshega lehaaza Tu mujhe bakhsh de is liye keh mai apne nafs par kiye huwe gunaho’n ka iqraar karta hu aur Tere azeem gunah ko koi dur nahi kar sakta.", "Urdu": "میرے چہرہ نے بندگی اور غلامی کی حالت میں تیرا سجدہ کیا، تیرے علاوہ کوئی حقیقی خدا نہیں ہے، تو ہر چیز سے پہلے ہے اور ہر چیز کے بعد بھی تو ہی ہے، میں تیرے سامنے ہوں، میری پیشانی تیرے ہاتھ (اختیار) میں ہے، لہٰذا تو مجھے بخش دے، یقینًا بڑے گناہ کو تیرے علاوہ کوئی نہیں بخشے گا لہٰذا تو مجھے بخش دے اس لئے کہ میں اپنے نفس پر کیے ہوئے گناہوں کا إقرار کرتا ہوں اور تیرے عظیم گناہ کو کوئی دور نہیں کر سکتا۔", "RArabic": "SAJADA LAKA WAJHEE TA-A’BBODAWN WA RIQQAN LAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANTA HAQQAN HAQQAN AL-AWWALO QABLA KULLE SHAY-IN WAL AAKHERO BA’DA KULLE SHAY-IN WA HAA ANAA ZAA BAYNA YADAYKA NAASEYATEE BEYADEKA FAGH-FIR LEE INNAHU LAA YAGHFERUZ ZANBAL A’ZEEMA GHAYROKA FAGHFIR LEE FA-INNEE MOQIRRUN BEZONOOBEE A’LAA NAFSEE WA LAA YADFA-U’Z ZANBAL A’ZEEMA GHAYROKA.", "ArabicText1": "سَجَدَ لَكَ وَجْہِیْ تَعَبُّدًا وَرِقًّا لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اَنْتَ حَقًّا حَقًّا اَلْاَوَّلُ قَبْلَ كُلِّ شَیْءٍ وَالْآخِرُ بَعْدَ كُلِّ شَیْءٍ وَہَا اَنَا ذَا بَیْنَ یَدَیْكَ نَاصِیَتِیْ بِیَ